de.nec.nle.siafu.output
Interface SimulatorOutputPrinter

All Known Implementing Classes:
CSVPrinter, NullPrinter
public interface SimulatorOutputPrinter

The interface to be implemented by the simulator outputs.

The simulator will call the printIteration method at the end of each iteration. It is then up to the particular implementation of the OutputPrinter whether to register this iteration, what information of it and how.

Author:
Miquel Martin
